{"tid":1624630,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非其實同樣重要","createTime":"2019-10-05T04:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T05:10:51.000Z","uid":261073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c25e39ae19153923f96071664c9c6d4679155912","tid":1624630,"uid":261073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:25:42.000Z","msg":"見到好多post話依家和理非已經無用,因為100/200萬人出政府都視若無睹<br />\n<br />\n但我想講和理非無用, 但其實勇武既作用都不大<br />\n1. 我地行動<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">升級左</span></span>, 每星期都有抗爭, 好似尋晚搞到咁大,各區開花,但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無動搖到政府半點地位</span></span>,林鄭就匿埋 有咩就叫警察出黎對我地 佢就安坐家中 請對準政權! 我地既訴求冇回應到 蒙面法都冇撤到 無錯我地係傷左幾隻狗,但記住我地既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目的係5大訴求</span></span>!!勇武左咁多次,5大訴求,無樣回應到<br />\n<br />\n2. 勇武人數愈來愈少,再搞都只係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">消耗戰</span></span> 勇武愈多 佢只會拉愈多人 愈多手足受傷 一黎我地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">武器上已經輸左</span></span> 人地有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真槍</span></span> TG 海綿彈 二黎好多<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前線有經驗勇武已經比人拉左</span></span>, 新手勇武未必夠打, 形勢對我地呢邊<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">極不利</span></span><br />\n<br />\n勇武無用,唔通和理非就有用?<br />\n3. 可以話2者作用都不大,既然係咁,點解唔簡個<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">傷亡少, 多人支持</span></span>既抗爭方式,要記住我地係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">長期抗爭</span></span>,同佢鬥長命,唔係靠一味衝就係最好既方法!!<br />\n<br />\n4. 和理非活動 絕大部分香港人都會撐 近來抗爭方式都偏勇武, 放火私了,其實令好多和理非都卻步,就算佢地唔割蓆,<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">考慮到安全問題都已經唔會出黎</span></span>,至少各區set rb已經令好多巴士入唔到 走唔到 擔心冇車返屋企自然唔敢出 人數已經少左一大埋, <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要贏, 一定要人多, 一定要民意</span></span><br />\n<br />\n係呢個時間講和理非 可能好難聽 但請大家冷靜諗下之後路向 一尾靠衝只係成功<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">比政府挑釁到</span></span>,佢就係想我地係呢3日End game!我地就唔可以比佢地得逞"},{"pid":"beea741372fc71a1b417a1e3fca2a491732a49f5","tid":1624630,"uid":261073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:33:42.000Z","msg":"自推10次!!"},{"pid":"3330cd1896f513b6e743ee903818fb66f76fe681","tid":1624630,"uid":261073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:34:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50a5995565ad6f40021052f7c5545243fc13d188","tid":1624630,"uid":261073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:34:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ff10f6a0eb8f78d4b6fecbea00c90360c730e5d","tid":1624630,"uid":261073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:35:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f45d5a0aa0252362dcaadd13624ff8756d457a2","tid":1624630,"uid":261073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:36:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d32107fa8375dd08cc8ed67ef71e17f295c4d3b8","tid":1624630,"uid":261073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:10:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ffc167144a99cc812a792fe50cea87e163dabc90","tid":1624630,"uid":261073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:10:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6394fb33fc3da7a0b24706963597a2ef9faf68a1","tid":1624630,"uid":261073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:10:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"132ac98a4a96882f3044fe7411b7e0a69407f22b","tid":1624630,"uid":261073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:10:51.000Z","msg":"推"}]}